        <item>
            <title>【教學】CrowdStrike 讓 Windows blue screen 藍屏開不到機解決方法</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/windows-blue-screen-%e8%97%8d%e5%b1%8f%e9%96%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%88%b0%e6%a9%9f%e8%a7%a3%e6%b1%ba%e6%96%b9%e6%b3%95%e6%95%99%e5%ad%b8-%e5%88%aa%e9%99%a4%e6%9c%89%e5%95%8f%e9%a1%8c%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=windows-blue-screen-%25e8%2597%258d%25e5%25b1%258f%25e9%2596%258b%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%2588%25b0%25e6%25a9%259f%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e6%25b1%25ba%25e6%2596%25b9%25e6%25b3%2595%25e6%2595%2599%25e5%25ad%25b8-%25e5%2588%25aa%25e9%2599%25a4%25e6%259c%2589%25e5%2595%258f%25e9%25a1%258c%25e6%2596%2587%25e4%25bb%25b6</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/windows-blue-screen-%e8%97%8d%e5%b1%8f%e9%96%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%88%b0%e6%a9%9f%e8%a7%a3%e6%b1%ba%e6%96%b9%e6%b3%95%e6%95%99%e5%ad%b8-%e5%88%aa%e9%99%a4%e6%9c%89%e5%95%8f%e9%a1%8c%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 08:12:35 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1251473</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在 7 月 19 日一款名為 CrowdStrike 的防毒軟件引起全球 Windows 災難，因為好多廠機都安裝了這款應用程式。全球多國用家面對 Windows 開機出現藍屏的問題。有專家就建議幾個步驟，如果電腦中招，可以跟著這些步驟解決問題。</p><p>消息指 CrowdStrike 工程部已經確定與此問題相關的內容部署，現在用家可依照以下步驟解決問題：</p><h2>將 Windows 進入安全模式或 Windows 恢復環境。</h2><p>（如電腦開機黑畫面或入不到 Windows，「開機見到手提電腦開機畫面（如電腦廠 logo）長按電源按鈕 10 秒關機＞開電源按鈕一下開機＞見到手提電腦開機畫面長按電源按鈕 10 秒關機＞開電源按鈕一下開機＞見到手提電腦開機畫面長按電源按鈕 10 秒關機」讓電腦認識你多次開機失敗，之後再次開機就可進入圖中的選單畫面）詳細可參考這個 <a href="https://support.microsoft.com/zh-hk/windows/在-windows-中以安全模式啟動電腦-92c27cff-db89-8644-1ce4-b3e5e56fe234">Windows 支援頁面</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251479" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1088-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1088-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1088-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲開機後選 Troubleshoot</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251481" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_10892-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_10892-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_10892-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇 Advanced options</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251482" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1091-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1091-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1091-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲按 Restart 重新啟動電腦</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251483" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1092-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1092-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1092-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在重啟電腦後的「啟動設定」選單選「5) 啟用安全模式 (含網路功能)」</p><p>在開啟安全模式後，利用檔案總管打開 C:\Windows\System32\drivers\CrowdStrike 目錄。找到符合 &#8220;C-00000291*.sys&#8221; 的文件，並刪除它。最後正常啟動主機便可回復原狀。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/crowdstrike/comments/1e6vmkf/bsod_error_in_latest_crowdstrike_update/">Reddit</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/windows-blue-screen-%e8%97%8d%e5%b1%8f%e9%96%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%88%b0%e6%a9%9f%e8%a7%a3%e6%b1%ba%e6%96%b9%e6%b3%95%e6%95%99%e5%ad%b8-%e5%88%aa%e9%99%a4%e6%9c%89%e5%95%8f%e9%a1%8c%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6/fun-tech/">【教學】CrowdStrike 讓 Windows blue screen 藍屏開不到機解決方法</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
