            <title>加強版多啦 A 夢無人機匯演明晚再現維港，官方公佈最佳觀賞位置</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/doraemon100-tour-in-hk-again/hottopic/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=doraemon100-tour-in-hk-again</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/doraemon100-tour-in-hk-again/hottopic/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 06:24:15 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中熱話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活娛樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[航拍]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[叮噹]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[多啦 A 夢]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[無人機匯演]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1251418</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">全球首場多啦 A 夢無人機匯演早前於 5 月 25 日在香港上演，反應非常熱烈並宣佈舉行第二次匯演。官方稱是次匯演為「加強版」，加入了新登場的彩蛋畫面和驚喜互動，乘坐着時光機的多啦 A 夢將與一眾好友再度出現在維港上空。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251419 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451808512_1008884457-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451808512_1008884457-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451808512_1008884457.jpg 719w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/100Doraemon/posts/1008891260633939">Doraemon 100</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">匯演將於明晚 7:30 pm 尖東維港上空舉行，預計表演內容大約 10 分鐘，官方更公開了匯演的最佳觀賞位置。表演當晚尖東將實施封路及人流管制措施，將會封閉梳士巴利道部分行車路段（東行及西行）和附近一帶的道路。大會建議市民可以到兩個最佳觀賞位置，分別是尖沙咀海濱公園（尖東海傍）以及封閉後的梳士巴利道（東行）部分行車路段。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251420 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451436245_1008884537-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451436245_1008884537-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451436245_1008884537.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/100Doraemon/posts/1008891260633939">Doraemon 100 </a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">天文台正考慮今日下午至晚上發出一號戒備信號，明晚的多啦 A 夢無人機匯演亦有機會因天氣關係受到影響，有計劃觀賞匯演的大家一定要密切留意官方在 <a href="https://www.facebook.com/100Doraemon">Facebook</a> 和 <a href="https://www.instagram.com/doraemon100_tour/">Instagram</a> 上的最新消息。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E7%86%B1%E9%BB%9E/article/20240719/s00024/1720523239251/%E5%A4%9A%E5%95%A6a%E5%A4%A2%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E5%8C%AF%E6%BC%94%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E7%89%887%E6%9C%8820%E6%97%A5%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C-%E5%A4%9A%E5%95%A6a%E5%A4%A2%E4%B9%98%E6%99%82%E5%85%89%E6%A9%9F%E7%8F%BE%E5%B0%96%E6%9D%B1%E5%A4%9C%E7%A9%BA%E3%80%90%E9%99%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E8%A7%80%E8%B3%9E%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%91?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR3KdFobUX7feNRK-LH4oHrUw4JvHAlkyCPSo7nea3t2EdmzSplBN5Nf7Iw_aem_ESztLzvSLlcaqknRVAetBw">明報</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/100Doraemon/videos/993424982379583/">Doraemon 100</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/05/doraemon-4/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">多啦 A 夢無人機匯演「加強版」　新內容及彩蛋 +表演日期</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/28/doraemon-3/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">江玉歡：無人機表演比煙火更具潛力，可在背景較暗的環境進行</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/doraemon100-tour-in-hk-again/hottopic/">加強版多啦 A 夢無人機匯演明晚再現維港，官方公佈最佳觀賞位置</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
