        <item>
            <title>Diablo IV 新資料片《憎恨之軀》初步試玩心得分享 :　「魂靈師」玩法超多變</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/vessel-of-hatred-preview/game-channel/game-review/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=vessel-of-hatred-preview</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/vessel-of-hatred-preview/game-channel/game-review/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[天恩]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 05:15:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲評測]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1251314</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小編有幸率先體驗《暗黑破壞神 4》（Diablo IV）最新資料片《憎恨之軀》（Vessel of Hatred）及全新職業「魂靈師」（Spiritborn）。現在就為大家分享一下這次重大 DLC 的新職業、地圖及心得。</p><h2><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0345-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251392" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0345-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0345-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0345-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></h2><h2>相關短片:</h2><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="Diablo IV 新資料片《憎恨之軀》初步試玩心得分享" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/986969305?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/diablo-iv-3/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《Diablo IV》新資料片  Vessel of Hatred 專訪，遊戲總監: 教你魂靈師如何搭配「最強傷害組合」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/diablo-iv-2/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《Diablo IV》新資料片 Vessel of Hatred 新職業: 魂靈師，如同隨時「轉職」 坦、法、僧侶、俠盜集一身</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/diablo-iv-vessel-of-hatred/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Diablo IV 首個資料片 10 月推出　《憎恨之軀》將加入新職業和地圖等</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>「魂靈師」　尤如四合一新職業</h2><p>「魂靈師」這個新職業可以召喚四種魂靈守護者：蜈蚣、巨猩、獵豹及飛鷹。每種守護者都有其特色和技能樹，玩家可以選擇兩個來獲得其被動加成。試玩了四個預設的魂靈師，等級限制在 30 級。雖未能體驗後期內容，但初步感受良好。以下是對每個守護者建構的簡單評價：</p><p><strong>蜈蚣，試玩感</strong></p><p>主打持續傷害（DOT），可同時造成傷害及治療自身。筆者最喜愛的一個，持續傷害的玩法流暢，技能效果華麗，感覺非常強大。不過整個畫面都是毒綠色及「特別」音效就不是每個人都喜歡。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114910.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251385" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114910-694x427.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="427" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114910-694x427.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114910.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="魂靈守護者「蜈蚣」技能施放預覽" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/986427384?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><strong>巨猩，試玩感</strong></p><p>偏向防禦，擁有高坦度和反擊能力，適合喜愛肉盾玩法的玩家。防禦力和反擊能力極高，遊玩時宛如一個野蠻人坦克。出招時感覺到地震是四款之中打擊感最強的。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122527.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251406" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122527-694x410.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="410" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122527-694x410.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122527.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="魂靈守護者「巨猩」技能施放預覽" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/986426813?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><strong>獵豹，試玩感</strong></p><p>專注於快速多次打擊和高機動性，類似潛行者的玩法。機動性高，打擊速度快，因為需要堆疊大招所以要不停清怪，玩起來節奏感強又爽，但缺點是防太低易死，solo 不太建議用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122237.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251405" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122237-694x464.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122237-694x464.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719122237.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="魂靈守護者「獵豹」技能施放預覽" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/986427697?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br /><strong>飛鷹，試玩感</strong></p><p>擅長中距離攻擊，有來回飛行的羽毛攻擊技能。但相較其他三個守護者，感覺略遜一籌，令我想起法師 teleport ，技能多數針對單體傷害，用來打小王及 boss 比較合適，反為依靠大招範圍清小怪</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115241.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251381" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115241-694x418.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="418" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115241-694x418.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115241.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="魂靈守護者「飛鷹」技能施放預覽" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/986427020?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><h2>技能混合才是精綷</h2><p>每個魂靈守護者都有獨特技能和裝備搭配，玩法多變，玩家可以混合不同守護者的技能，創造出獨特的建構。筆者嘗試了混合不同魂靈守護者的技能。將蜈蚣的持續傷害技能與巨猩的高防禦技能結合，可以創造出一個既能造成大量傷害又非常耐打的角色。這樣的組合讓你在面對大量敵人時仍能保持生存，並且逐漸削弱敵人。</p><p>我同時試了「強攻」型將獵豹混合蜈蚣，清怪超快但要份外小心，因為「皮薄」需要留意血量，小編用這個組合經常要飲紅水。如果不作混合，也可能主副選相同的魂靈去大大強化本身特色。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114622.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251376" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114622-555x580.jpg" alt="" width="555" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114622-555x580.jpg 555w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719114622.jpg 861w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 555px" /></a></p><h2>終極技能及新機制</h2><p>每個魂靈守護者都有其獨特的終極技能大招（Ultimate），無論是巨猩的持續傷害和屏障，還是獵豹的高速攻擊和重置冷卻時間，都令遊戲過程更加豐富。魂靈師還引入了幾個新機制：</p><p>決心（Resolve）：增強防禦的效果，每受到一次傷害就會失去一層，但只要還有層數，就能提供 20% 的傷害減免。<br />
不受阻礙（Unhindered）：可穿越敵人，移動速度不會被減慢。<br />
狂怒（Ferocity）：增加攻擊速度的效果，可疊加。</p><p>基本上這個設定逼使玩家要主動出擊才能獲得最大得著，如果在團中瑟縮一角對保命力和輸出都大打節扣，是高風險高回報的玩法，比較適合節奏明快的玩家</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115850.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251378" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115850-429x580.jpg" alt="" width="429" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115850-429x580.jpg 429w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240719115850.jpg 665w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 429px" /></a></p><h2>新地圖視覺效果出色</h2><p>除了魂靈師，小編還體驗一些新區域和據點。視覺效果非常出色，尤其是一個充滿燈籠和光影對比強烈的據點令人印象深刻。玩家需要攜帶燈籠照亮黑暗區域，並在戰鬥中利用光照機制對付敵人，大大增加了遊戲的策略性和趣味性。這種氣氛已經令你回想起 Diablo 2 ，同時你又真的聽到一些 D2 懷舊 BGM，令老玩家倍感親切。</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/diablo-iv-3/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《Diablo IV》新資料片  Vessel of Hatred 專訪，遊戲總監: 教你魂靈師如何搭配「最強傷害組合」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/diablo-iv-2/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《Diablo IV》新資料片 Vessel of Hatred 新職業: 魂靈師，如同隨時「轉職」 坦、法、僧侶、俠盜集一身</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/diablo-iv-vessel-of-hatred/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Diablo IV 首個資料片 10 月推出　《憎恨之軀》將加入新職業和地圖等</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>總結 : 值得再次投入</h2><p>整體而言，魂靈師這個新職業帶來了全新的遊戲機制，多樣性和靈活性極高。玩家可以根據自己的喜好，自由搭配不同的魂靈守護者技能，創造出獨特且強大的建構。感覺就像是四個新職業合而為一，每個守護者都有其獨特風格和玩法。<br />
雖然這次只體驗到前期內容，但已令人期待滿滿。如果你對這個新職業感興趣，不妨等待更多資訊發布後再作決定。</p><h1 style="text-align: center;"></h1><div style="padding:56.25% 0 0 0;position:relative;"><iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/986969305?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;" title="Diablo IV 新資料片《憎恨之軀》初步試玩心得分享"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><h2>後記: 總部參觀充滿遊戲色彩</h2><p>除了試玩小編還參觀暴雪總部，館內的大型雕像令人印象深刻，還有專門的博物館展示遊戲開發歷程。目前展示的是《Warcraft Rumble》的內容，此前曾展出《暗黑破壞神 4》的相關資料。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0320-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251399" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0320-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0320-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0320-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0324-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251398" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0324-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0324-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0324-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0348-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251396" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0348-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0348-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0348-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0346-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251397" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0346-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0346-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0346-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0357-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251395" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0357-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0357-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_0357-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/diablo-iv-3/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《Diablo IV》新資料片  Vessel of Hatred 專訪，遊戲總監: 教你魂靈師如何搭配「最強傷害組合」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/diablo-iv-2/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《Diablo IV》新資料片 Vessel of Hatred 新職業: 魂靈師，如同隨時「轉職」 坦、法、僧侶、俠盜集一身</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/diablo-iv-vessel-of-hatred/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Diablo IV 首個資料片 10 月推出　《憎恨之軀》將加入新職業和地圖等</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/vessel-of-hatred-preview/game-channel/game-review/">Diablo IV 新資料片《憎